WEBVTT

00:13:59.412 --> 00:14:03.422
Moja soba, moje knjige, ja,

00:14:04.815 --> 00:14:08.528
sve što mi je donosilo osmeh.

00:14:09.895 --> 00:14:14.182
O, o, imao sam toliko snova

00:14:14.182 --> 00:14:17.777
koji je trebalo da se ostvare."

00:14:19.105 --> 00:14:21.633
Dakle evo moje poente:

00:14:21.633 --> 00:14:23.712
ne investirati u izbeglice

00:14:23.712 --> 00:14:27.033
je ogromna propuštena prilika.

00:14:29.073 --> 00:14:31.219
Ostavite ih napuštenim,